        <p style="text-align: left;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 16px;"><strong>Changes to our privacy policy</strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 16px;">Any changes that we make to our privacy policy in the future will be posted on this page and, where appropriate, notified to you by email. Please check frequently to see any updates or changes to our privacy policy.</p>
